## âš™ï¸ How It Works

### 1ï¸âƒ£ Search Phase

The script searches PubMed Central (PMC) using prognosis-related keywords:

* prognosis / prognostic
* survival / mortality
* outcome / outcomes
* recurrence / relapse
* staging / risk

### 2ï¸âƒ£ Download Phase

* Fetches full-text XML articles
* Extracts title, abstract, and body paragraphs
* Filters short or low-content articles

### 3ï¸âƒ£ Cleaning Phase

Removes:

* Reference markers ([1], (2), etc.)
* Figure and table mentions
* URLs
* Extra whitespace

### 4ï¸âƒ£ Storage Phase

Saves cleaned text into structured `.txt` files.

